sql:
SELECT name, SUM(volume_24h) AS total_volume_24h
FROM cryptocurrencies
WHERE symbol = 'BTC';

external_knowledge:
- Actively traded in the past month refers to having at least one trade in the last month; 
- Average 24-hour price increase refers to the percentage change in the cryptocurrency price over a 24-hour period, averaged over the last 7 days; 
- Top-performing cryptocurrencies are those with the highest average price increase.
